text: Glossop is a small town in the Borough of High Peak west Derbyshire in England. Glossop is a market town and as of 2014 had a population of around 33,000 but as of 2001 Glossop had a population of 32,428.https://www.visionofbritain.org.uk/unit_page.jsp?u_id=10055416&c;_id=10001043 Viewed on 16/07/2022https://www.visionofbritain.org.uk/data_cube_table_page.jsp?data_theme=T_POP&data;_cube=N_TPop&u;_id=10054874&c;_id=10001043&add;=N Viewed on 16/07/2022 == References == Category:Towns in Derbyshire
